import matplotlib.pyplot as plt # plt 
import matplotlib.image as mpimg # mpimg 
import os

path = '/Users/leon/Desktop/xlab/Group_43/images/data_files/'
plt.rcParams['figure.dpi'] = 120 #

for i in range(1, 68):
    pic = os.path.join(path, str(i)+'.png')
    img=mpimg.imread(pic)
    plt.imshow(img)
    plt.title('A1Benchmark/real_' + str(i) + '.csv')
    plt.show()
